<article id="post-1084" class="post-1084 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-costa-rica category-general tag-butterflies tag-san-jose tag-shopping tag-traffic">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/09/butterflies-and-getting-lost/" rel="bookmark">Butterflies and getting lost</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>You can only stay around Santa Ana for so long before you start to feel a little caged in. And given that Alex and Mi Pequeña Niña are here all day, every day, there was a distinct need to explore a bit beyond our bounds. So Saturday morning (yes, I know this is a little late, I&#8217;ve intentionally been keeping away from my computer this weekend) we went off in search of adventure.  <br />
And butterflies.  <br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/09/butterflies-and-getting-lost/#more-1084" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;Butterflies and getting lost&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/09/butterflies-and-getting-lost/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2008-09-07T22:51:35-06:00">7 September 2008</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/costa-rica/" rel="category tag">Costa Rica</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/butterflies/" rel="tag">butterflies</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/san-jose/" rel="tag">san jose</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/shopping/" rel="tag">shopping</a>, <a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/traffic/" rel="tag">traffic</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2008/09/butterflies-and-getting-lost/#comments">1 Comment<span class="screen-reader-text"> on Butterflies and getting lost</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
